reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Gives a clean look
reviews.reviewText: These extensions leave a clean look. The wires from my power supply were nice just not as nice. The power supply wires have a braided fabric sleeve till about 3 inches from the plug. This it has a zip tie that is shrink wrapped than about an inch of shinny coated plastic wires. With these extensions each wire is fabric covered all the way to the plug with wire combs keeping them with a clean appearance. Its not much of a change but does improve its appearance. At the same time depending upon your computer case the space behind could be limited for longer wires along with the connectors. My case is a Be Quiet DX500 and it is very snug in the back with the added wires.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are better quality than the "garden variety" of extensions. Every part of these is premium. the sockets and plugs, wire, and attached spreaders. I also like they are made of stiffer structure than many others. The set I previously had on my desktop was limp and would just lie wherever. With these, you can bend them, and they will remain in place on their own, thereby making a much more attractive and cleaner installation.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These cable extensions look great and add a touch of refinement to the appearance of your PC. Instead of those plain plastic power supply cables, you can add a color matching or highlight color to your system. Installation was easy and the pre installed cable combs save time and effort for installation.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Cable Upgrade That Sparkles!
reviews.reviewText: I recently got these white PSU cables for my PC build, and I'm thrilled with the results! The easy management and gold-plated connectors add a touch of elegance to my rig. The nylon sleeves not only look great but also make cable organization a breeze. Used them to spruce up my setup, and I couldn't be happier. Highly recommended for anyone looking to add a clean and polished look to their PC!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Flexible, nice combs
reviews.reviewText: Extensions are flexible with nice combs, including a captive comb on the ATX power cable. I'd prefer 3x PCIe and 1x EPS power instead of 2x of each.
